pr_body:
Description
---
Please refer to #221 for a full description of this "epic". It consists of bringing our clustering visualisations into WellcomeML. It has two user stories

Closes #293: Build method to visualise `wellcomeml.ml.TextClustering`
Closes #294: Style plots

This was part of Google Summer of Code. A report and nice pictures of the visualisations are here https://gist.github.com/federikovi/0ff5f376105e3111d624d935758cded3 

❗❗❗ When reviewing please ignore all files inside `/docs`, except `docs/clustering.rst` - all others are generated automatically

Checklist
---

- [x] Added link to Github issue or Trello card
- [x] Added tests
